Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本解放戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.68,0:00:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了摧毀這支AREA-11最大的武裝勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯內莉婭總督對成田連山展開了包圍作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在以壓倒性戰力為傲的布里塔尼亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以為大勢已定之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑之騎士團開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,利用紅蓮二式的輻射波動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使山頂的地下水脈瞬間大爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,山體崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不論日本解放戰線還是布里塔尼亞軍的主力部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全被捲入泥石洪流中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失去主戰力的柯內莉婭部隊 孤立無援
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以期扭轉戰局的ZERO率領黑之騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.80,0:00:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向著柯內莉婭進發 然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人類總是相信自己將會勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:01:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然而在時間與命運的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,『相信』這種行為 過於徒然 過於虛幻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 11
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}成田攻防戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我軍傷亡如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,部隊20%的機體沒有回應了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,20%?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來很難正常指揮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是馬裡遜隊 無法與阿歷克斯將軍取得聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只能認為第2師團全滅…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,羅伊德先生 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:02:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 極其不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:02:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不自然?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:02:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然還未確認
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過有情報表示黑之騎士團出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你啦 說不定會有出場機會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,羅伊德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太不謹慎了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要我教教你嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之不論如何 我們也只能根據參謀部收集情報的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再決定相應的對策了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總督沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身處崩塌洪流之外 所以平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是因為身後的後援部隊隨意行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在處於孤立狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,純血派到底在搞什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 啟動啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會輸給ELEVEN!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至高無上的布里塔尼亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,丘威爾卿!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 紅蓮前往預定地點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其餘的人從這裡突破 生擒柯內莉婭!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 我們能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死守住這裡!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杉山 還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:03:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該死 幹掉他們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對 行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有在這場戰爭中存活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們才能成為戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,考驗就在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,純血派牽制住他們了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在維蕾塔卿的指揮下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就趁此良機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓總督撤退到後方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓空軍掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總督後面有什麼人正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各機 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無賴·改  出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這次山崩是人為造成的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們應該能突入柯內莉婭的背後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,俘虜柯內莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正是報七年前的一箭之仇的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,賭上吾等『四聖劍』的名譽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,保護殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,包圍她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本解放戰線嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,斬擊包圍陣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,承知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要認為這只是普通的無賴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我想起七年前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和那時可不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我們也有KnightMare呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下 這裡交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.53,0:05:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請暫時撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就採取防守反擊策略
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉爾弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊交鋒一邊向Point-9移動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Point-9?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯內莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,脆弱的東西!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就這樣把ZERO牽制住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 還是讓卡蓮回來會比較好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在如果改變部署 計劃就作廢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此 但情況的確不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再這樣下去甚至會與親衛隊正面交鋒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像柯內莉婭在下面受到了奇襲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪個部隊的行動?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我們 好像是解放戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有明白我意圖的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼這樣應該可以拖住親衛隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少將閣下 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,籐堂 等著你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,閣下 請在你那邊投入全部兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能贏他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若能牽制住布里塔尼亞主力的話就能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正是扭轉乾坤的好時機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說在AREA-11有一個人同時具備 將軍之才 與 騎士之能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道這人就是那個籐堂?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏在這種時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何都要和柯內莉婭總督會合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 敵人的大本營就在眼前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 撤退時背後受襲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會造成巨大的損失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果失去了公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這場戰鬥就徹底失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是… 是!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尤菲米婭副總督
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓這艘G1也出擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,將總督…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是… 吉爾弗德隊長無法移動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就意味著柯內莉婭總督的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡還設有野戰醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以及周圍來避難的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 這艘G1基地是本陣的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總督嚴令 無論發生什麼事都不得移動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此…所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特別派遣嚮導技術部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無禮的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是隨軍的局外人 乖乖待一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個… 確實是這樣 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此我們很困擾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,閒得慌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尤菲米婭副總督
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請對特派下令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別以為我們不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不就是想要救出總督的功績嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果僅憑一機就能改變戰局的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都不會辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還只不過是個NUMBERS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說啦 讓我們試試也無妨嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使失敗了你們也沒什麼損失嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 有在聽嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 那就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是 定不負所望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙 真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,散開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯內莉婭怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果ZERO是預想中那種人的話 此時一定會出手的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只有相信他了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO改變行進路線了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在打算順道去援助你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,更重要的是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我路線情報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是ZERO他們的預測路線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑之騎士團正前往我們引誘籐堂他們去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯內莉婭殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽見了  吉爾弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嚮導兵器  Z01  Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用山道速滑板(SandBoot)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用最大戰速沿液狀斜面上升
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救援總督
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 想問你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你極端討厭有人死亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:08:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但你卻加入軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不讓他人死亡 我才加入軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種矛盾 總有一天會害死你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Lancelot 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯內莉婭!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就憑你這卑賤之人?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不是普通的CUSTOM機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[CUSTOM機：指一般機體的強化機種]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能聽見嗎 柯內莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經被將軍了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該歡慶我們的再會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 在此之前 希望你向我們投降
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有事想要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,順帶一提 援軍是趕不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我贏了哦 柯內莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真愚蠢啊 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要打倒這傢伙 就能殺出生路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是靈巧的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然從背後偷襲?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦? 你是想說你們的作戰不卑鄙嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在重整隊形前受到夾擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣可無法趕到公主殿下的身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把敵人的援軍擊潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,轉換為『旋回活殺自在陣』
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,承知
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去柯內莉婭殿下會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉爾弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之騎士吉爾弗德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你與達爾頓一起輔佐尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕不投降
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只會戰鬥至最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯…柯內莉婭大人!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 無聊的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一如既往的亂來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然用VARIS擊毀山體間的障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總督 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我來救援了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是特派?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰允許的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那台Lancelot的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂… 難道是那台KnightMare?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對 是新宿和河口湖那時的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了 又是那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅蓮二式去毀掉那台白色機體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙的突破力很礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我來對付ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新宿的仇就在此…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有能與Lancelot匹敵的高速度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要打倒這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就憑這種武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,擋下了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯… 還好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扇 紅蓮怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,右手不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要修理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全軍 向撤退地點移動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再下去會成為消耗戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總督
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你去追ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是能源(Energy Filler)用完了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 就這麼撤退真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,勝利已是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只得把日本解放戰線作為誘餌以安全逃離嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭這種說法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人不是遊戲的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO應該也沒有這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,否則
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也不過是他的棋子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他對於布里塔尼亞的憤怒是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知曉憤怒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該也知曉悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,報告特派指揮車(Head Trailer)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發現ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始捕獲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 你有恩於我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也有不少人因你的行動而得救
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很清楚許多ELEVEN在暗中協助你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 你的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是錯誤的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是  新宿的…  密封艙裡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不准對這個人出手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是… ZERO的同伴?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你想做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對方可是KnightMare啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你死了我會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然只是間接接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一試的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該已經死了的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不想那樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我… 我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 難道你對駕駛員使用Geass?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是讓他看一些震驚的影像(Shock Image)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我也不知道他看到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是你  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在不能動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼不斷地欠你人情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 現在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼 和上次不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,停…停下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要進入…我的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…的心… 被徹底打開了!…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能那麼做啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛…剛才那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快走啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要追
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的行動被壓制了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就此與少將會合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,協助他們逃離此地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下 我立刻趕來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉爾弗德 通報全軍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,準備撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒有理由繼續賭上我們將士的生命了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,維持戰鬥態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,緩緩撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不承認
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次是我們輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞光是要對付解放戰線就已經竭盡全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 確實給了我們逃跑的機會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 ZERO呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無法和ZERO的無賴取得聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會被抓了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個女人 果然不是人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傷口的再生速度太不尋常了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在新宿時的確是被擊中了額頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是克洛維斯私下在研究的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和布里塔尼亞應該沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生理徵兆(vital sign)與人類相同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[vital sign：生理徵兆 如脈搏 呼吸 體溫 心跳等]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血液樣本稍後再調查
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傷口也拍下照片吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你終於叫了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是沒能抓住ZERO嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由於日本解放戰線撤退時設下了防衛線
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能混在其中逃脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總是能找到什麼作為盾牌來保護自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,樞木怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已回收完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由於要等到他的Energy Filler耗盡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以花了不少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,機體出了什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或許是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是陷入了暴走狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.46,0:19:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不像是皇兄部隊會出現的失態呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經幫你取出了碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傷口也清洗過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒必要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你救我根本沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你總是在些無聊的地方執著於尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過倒是因此知道了件有趣的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種興趣可真不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然偷聽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯的名字嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起C.C.更像人類的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說 像人類這種事根本就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:19:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今 名字什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,名字…什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就趁此良機說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才被你救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至今為止一直如此  以及Geass的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被感謝還是第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就向你要一份回禮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再叫一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像剛才那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一次就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要深情地 溫柔地 全心全意地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不夠溫柔 坦誠和體貼的心意也不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發音也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是 缺少溫暖的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個任性的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我是C.C.啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.19,0:21:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是軍人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說明部隊潰亂到這種程度了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是ORANGE啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來迎接的人來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的成員已經先行…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我非常重要的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不知道雪為什麼是白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.06,0:22:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但我覺得白色的雪很美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,將柯內莉婭逼入絕境的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.67,0:23:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了彌補這個缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.48,0:24:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能我自己必須跨越某種障礙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.68,0:24:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有黑之騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.43,0:24:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,勢必前往下一個既定的驛站
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.07,0:24:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為此 若有必要 我…
